<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Paul Fisher - Tangerine</title>
  <style>
    /* Fondo con degradado pastel animado */
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde2e4, #fad2e1, #e2ece9, #bee1e6);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradientMove 10s ease infinite;
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin: 0;
    }

    @keyframes gradientMove {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #ffffffcc;
      border-radius: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 380px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      border: 3px solid #f4b6c2;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #f08a8a;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .header h2 {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    img {
      width: 150px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 5px solid #fad2e1;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      transition: transform 0.5s;
    }

    img:hover {
      transform: rotate(-5deg) scale(1.05);
    }

    .info {
      background: #fdf6f9;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #f4b6c2;
    }

    .info p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .quote {
      background: #fce7f3;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 12px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      border: 1px dashed #f4b6c2;
    }

    .quote p {
      color: #555;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #f4a7b9;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #f08a8a;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Paul Fisher</h1>
      <h2>Character from <em>Tangerine</em> by Edward Bloor</h2>
    </div>

    <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/12/11/18/29/boy-5824401_1280.png" alt="Paul Fisher" />

    <div class="info">
      <p><strong>Full Name:</strong> Paul Fisher</p>
      <p><strong>Age:</strong> 12 years old</p>
      <p><strong>Lives in:</strong> Lake Windsor Downs, Florida</p>
      <p><strong>Family:</strong> Lives with his parents and older brother Erik</p>
      <p><strong>School:</strong> Tangerine Middle School</p>
      <p><strong>Likes:</strong> Soccer, honesty, and helping friends</p>
      <p><strong>Goal:</strong> To be brave and see the truth about his life</p>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
      <p>‚ÄúI can see things other people can‚Äôt.‚Äù</p>
    </div>

    <button class="btn">About Paul üí´</button>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>Made with üíï by Majo</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
